一、调用 GitLab Pipeline 并传入 variables
GitLab API：

POST /projects/:id/pipeline
Python 示例：
Python
import requests

gitlab_url = "https://gitlab.com/api/v4"
project_id = "123456"
token = "YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN"

url = f"{gitlab_url}/projects/{project_id}/pipeline"

data = {
    "ref": "main",
    "variables": [
        {"key": "TEST_DURATION", "value": "5"},
        {"key": "TEST_TYPE", "value": "load"}
    ]
}

headers = {
    "PRIVATE-TOKEN": token
}

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers, json=data)

print(response.json())
返回结果类似：
JSON
{
 "id": 789123,
 "iid": 45,
 "web_url": "https://gitlab.com/xxx/project/-/pipelines/789123",
 "status": "created"
}
你要的 pipeline地址就是

web_url
